@@TJvCopyError
<TITLEIMG TJvCopyError>
JVCLInfo
  GROUP=JVCL.Dialogs.Common
  FLAG=Component
Summary
  Displays a dialog box for errors encountered when copying a file.
Description
  This component is used to display a dialog box encountered when copying a file during a setup
  routine. It is a wrapper for the SetupCopyError API call.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.DiskName
Summary
  The name of the disk to prompt for.
Description
  This property contains the name of the disk the user will be prompted for.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.PathToSource

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.Execute
Summary
  Shows the dialog box.
Description
  This method shows the SetupCopyError dialog box.
Return value
  This method returns dsSuccess if the file has been found, dsCancel if the user pressed "Cancel",
  dsSkipFile if the user pressed "Skip File", and dsError if an error occurred.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.NewPath
Summary
  Contains the path chosen by the user.
Description
  This property contains the new path chosen by the user in the dialog box.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.PathToSource, TJvCopyError.SourceFile

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.PathToSource
Summary
  Default path to look for the file.
Description
  This property contains the initial contents for the combo box used to hold the user-selected path.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.DiskName

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.SourceFile
Summary
  File to look for.
Description
  This property contains the file that the user needs to provide the location for.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.NewPath, TJvCopyError.PathToSource

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.Style
Summary
  Flags used for modifying the dialog box.
Description
  These flags modify how the dialog box is presented to the user.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.TargetFile
Summary
  The target file for the copy operation.
Description
  This property contains the destination file of the copy operation.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.Win32ErrorCode

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCopyError.Win32ErrorCode
Summary
  Error code from the copy operation.
Description
  This property contains the Windows error code that occurred in the copy operation.
See Also
  TJvCopyError.TargetFile

